      "Movement across cross-chain bridges continues at a rapid pace, with the total value accelerated by 49% compared to the 30-day average, signaling intensified activity.",
      "On June 9th, Layerzero V2 facilitated $7.48 billion in transfers, following an even larger $22.65 billion on June 8th \u2014 a combined $30 billion in just two days.",
      "The PORTAL bridge also saw substantial activity, moving $2.05 billion on June 9th and $6.52 billion on June 8th, reflecting continued high capital flow.",
      "USDT remained a primary asset for cross-chain transfers, with $3.63 billion moved on June 9th and $7.19 billion on June 8th via the USDT0 bridge, underscoring its role in inter-chain liquidity.",
